title: The Protomen
description:
The Protomen were concieved in 1987, when a diminutive Mississippi child was given a gift for his kindergarten graduation ? A small grey cartridge with a rather misrepresentative cover art. At that moment, six other children, of varied statures and geographical locales, were also given these cartridges, and thus their grooming began. Sixteen years later, in the middle of the state of volunteers and under the tutelage of Doug Mitchell, their paths converged, their fates were made known, and their assembly was made complete.
